# Strapi CMS app placeholder.
#
# When you're ready to add Strapi:
#
#   1. cd apps && pnpm dlx create-strapi-app@latest cms --quickstart --no-run --typescript
#   2. Add to apps/cms/package.json:
#        "name": "@portfolio/cms"
#   3. The root pnpm-workspace.yaml already includes apps/* so it'll be picked up
#   4. Set STRAPI_URL + STRAPI_API_TOKEN in apps/web/.env.local
#
# Strapi Cloud alternative:
#   - Skip step 1, just point STRAPI_URL at your Cloud instance
